name: WebObjects Application
summary: Learn about .WOA files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Web addresses that include ".woa" in the URL are generated using WebObjects. However, WebObjects pages do not necessarily require the ".woa" extension.

description: Web application created with WebObjects, an enterprise framework developed by Apple; uses Java code and object-oriented design principles; can be deployed on any platform that supports Java programs.
